# CAM::SET_FOLLOW_VEHICLE_CAM_HIGH_ANGLE_MODE_THIS_UPDATE

## Summary
Overrides the state of the high-angle mode for the active follow vehicle camera for this update only

## Parameters
* **BOOL** state
